    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found anywhere. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled garage. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade example that needs absolutely nothing.",
